{
  "stem": "27770.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From this train, I would say half of them was dead already, because snow was falling us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No food.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Here a dead body on this side, and here a dead body on this side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the only thing that we could eat in these two days on the train, there was a special dish, they called it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's a little aluminum oval dish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It has a wire to hold it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And everybody took off from his shirt a piece made of string, and was connecting it to this particular dish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And while this train was running, we picked up snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This was the food what we-- this was our food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We arriving to Mauthausen approximately around 11 o'clock in the evening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Right away, they bring us in into a shower.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This is the first thing by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[GERMAN], we have to be clean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they give us hot shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They didn't ask if it's too hot or too cold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Hot like hell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "After the shower, you went through a selection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The selection was all done in a different style like in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "One guy was standing with a black pencil, and any person who passed by and he saw he's not anymore ready for work, he just made an X on his back, and this guy was already-- they didn't use their gas.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They used-- they electrocuted. 12 o'clock, we were finished with the shower.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They threw us outside on the snow naked and till morning, 6 o'clock, after a hot shower, hundreds there, or thousands, I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Probably a thousand there, sitting-- standing, not sitting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was-- you couldn't sit on the snow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Naked, after a hot shower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't even know if somebody got to catch a cold.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
